Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Entity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EnemyFish, PlayerFish

    public class Entity
extends Object
    An entity represents an entity in the game world. It has a movement speed, an alive state, and a sprite as a model.
    Author:
    Clinton Cao, Dmity Malarev, Matthijs Halvemaan, Sunwei Wang, Michiel Doesburg.
